content: yungalgo: Merged two PRs this week, including a significant CLI improvement PR #4031 that added over 21k lines and removed nearly 4k lines, focusing on plugin installation and GitHub authentication UX. The other merged PR #4004 (+129/-34 lines) validated and tested CLI command functionality, with both contributions showing a focus on enhancing the command-line interface. Active on 3 days this week with 11 commits across 14 modified files, demonstrating a balanced mix of bugfix work (55%) and other development tasks (45%).
